202
00:14:12,666 --> 00:14:15,282
♪A tear of hatred♪

203
00:14:15,610 --> 00:14:18,362
♪Falls onto fingertip near♪

204
00:14:18,554 --> 00:14:19,994
♪With obsession♪

205
00:14:19,994 --> 00:14:21,362
♪I mend the world's♪

206
00:14:21,402 --> 00:14:25,594
♪Ever-changing cracks♪
